about.summary: Backports and enhancements for the contextlib module

name: contextlib2
raw_recipe:
{%set name = "contextlib2" %}
{% set version = "0.5.4" %}
{%set hash_type = "sha256" %}
{%set hash_val = "710626cde569f51a87f216ff757fe60f5cd13ae8f8114706590510cd5649ce88" %}

package:
  name: {{ name }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  fn: {{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  {{ hash_type }}: {{ hash_val }}

build:
  script: python setup.py install
  number: 0

requirements:
  build:
    - python
    - setuptools

  run:
    - python

test:
  imports:
    - contextlib2

about:
  home: http://contextlib2.readthedocs.org
  license: PSF
  license_family: PSF
  license_file: LICENSE.txt
  summary: 'Backports and enhancements for the contextlib module'
  dev_url: https://github.com/jazzband/contextlib2
  doc_url: http://contextlib2.readthedocs.org

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - dopplershift
